==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Reperception
<hw>Re`per*cep"tion</hw> <pr>(r?`p?r-s?p"sh?n)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos>
<def>The act of perceiving again; a repeated perception of the same
object.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>No external praise can give me such a glow as my own solitary
<qex>reperception</qex> and ratification of what is fine.</q>
<rj><qau>Keats.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Repercuss</ent>⟦br⟧
